{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparisons-with-the-logical-and-operator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Poredjenja sa Logickim AND Operatorom","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ponekad je potrebno proveriti vise uslova odjednom. <dfn>Logicki AND</dfn> operator (<code>&#x26;&#x26;</code>) vraca <code>true</code> samo ako su <dfn>operandi</dfn> i levo i desno od njega tacni.</p>\n<p>Isto ponasanje se moze dobiti ugnjezdenjem jednog <code>if</code> iskaza unutar drugog.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">if (num > 5) {\n  if (num &#x3C; 10) {\n    return \"Yes\";\n  }\n}\nreturn \"No\";\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovaj kod vraca <code>Yes</code> ako je <code>num</code> veci od <code>5</code> i manji od <code>10</code>. Ista logika moze se napisati koristeci <dfn>logicki AND</dfn> operator.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">if (num > 5 &#x26;&#x26; num &#x3C; 10) {\n  return \"Yes\";\n}\nreturn \"No\";\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d8","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Zamenite dva <code>if</code> iskaza jednim iskazom koji koristi <code>&#x26;&#x26;</code> i vraca string <code>Yes</code> ako je <code>val</code> manje ili jednako <code>50</code> i vece ili jednako <code>25</code>. U suprotnom, treba da vrati string <code>No</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16799,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparisons-with-the-logical-and-operator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function testLogicalAnd(val) {\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n  if (val) {\n    if (val) {\n      return \"Yes\";\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Only change code above this line\n  return \"No\";\n}\n\ntestLogicalAnd(10);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da koristite operator <code>&#x26;&#x26;</code> jednom</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/&&/g).length === 1);"},{"text":"<p>Treba da imate samo jedan <code>if</code> iskaz</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/if/g).length === 1);"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalAnd(0)</code> treba da vrati string <code>No</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalAnd(0) === 'No');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalAnd(24)</code> treba da vrati string <code>No</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalAnd(24) === 'No');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalAnd(25)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Yes</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalAnd(25) === 'Yes');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalAnd(30)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Yes</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalAnd(30) === 'Yes');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalAnd(50)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Yes</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalAnd(50) === 'Yes');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalAnd(51)</code> treba da vrati string <code>No</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalAnd(51) === 'No');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalAnd(75)</code> treba da vrati string <code>No</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalAnd(75) === 'No');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalAnd(80)</code> treba da vrati string <code>No</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalAnd(80) === 'No');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"comparisons-with-the-logical-and-operator","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparisons-with-the-logical-or-operator","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-less-than-or-equal-to-operator","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d8","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparisons-with-the-logical-and-operator"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}